---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Referral Submitted - Nurture" description="Thank you for submitting a referral to Nurture Airbnb Property Management. We'll reach out to them within 24 hours.">
  <section class="thank-you-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="thank-you-card">
        <div class="success-icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="80" height="80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"></path>
            <polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1>Referral submitted!</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">We'll reach out to them within 24 hours and give them a free rental estimate.</p>

        <div class="next-steps">
          <h2>What Happens Next</h2>
          <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
              <span class="step-number">1</span>
              <div>
                <strong>We contact your referral</strong>
                <p>Our team reaches out within 24 hours to introduce Nurture and offer a free rental estimate.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <span class="step-number">2</span>
              <div>
                <strong>They get onboarded</strong>
                <p>If they decide to move forward, we handle everything from listing creation to their first booking.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
              <span class="step-number">3</span>
              <div>
                <strong>You get $500</strong>
                <p>Once your referral receives their first booking with us, you earn $500. No limit on how many people you can refer.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="another-referral">
          <p>Know someone else?</p>
          <a href="/referral" class="btn btn-primary">Submit Another Referral</a>
        </div>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <p>Questions? Reach us at:</p>
          <a href="tel:+16479578956" class="phone-link">647-957-8956</a>
        </div>

        <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline">Return to Homepage</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .thank-you-section {
    min-height: calc(100vh - 80px);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 4rem 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-background-alt) 0%, var(--color-background) 100%);
  }

  .thank-you-card {
    max-width: 600px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 3rem;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .success-icon {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary) 0%, var(--color-primary-dark) 100%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .thank-you-card h1 {
    font-size: 2.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .next-steps {
    background: var(--color-background-alt);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
  }

  .next-steps h2 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .step strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .step p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .another-referral {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .another-referral p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .contact-info {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-info p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .phone-link {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .phone-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-primary-dark);
  }

  .btn-outline {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-primary);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .btn-outline:hover {
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: white;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .thank-you-card {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }

    .thank-you-card h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }

    .next-steps {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
